      "text": "As it is writ-ten, Thou didst a-rise the third day from the tomb, O Christ, rais-ing al---so the fore-fa-ther of our race; for__ this cause doth all man--kind ex-tol Thee, whilst ac-claim--ing Thy Res-ur-rec-tion, chant-ing hymns of__ praise.__"
    }
  }
}